<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٩١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5614">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ زِيَادٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«أَخَذَ الْحَسَنُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ <span class="special">﵄</span> تَمْرَةً مِنْ تَمْرِ الصَّدَقَةِ، فَجَعَلَهَا فِي فِيهِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> كَِخْ كَِخْ. لِيَطْرَحَهَا،<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ قَالَ:</span> أَمَا شَعَرْتَ أَنَّا لَا نَأْكُلُ الصَّدَقَةَ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>